5. " (Refer Practical Vim Pg101 Link to Vimcasts episode)
" Easy expansion of active file directory
"`nnoremap <leader>ew :e <C-R>=expand('%:p:h').'/'<CR>`
" (Refer Practical Vim Pg101 Link to Vimcasts episode)
